Assigment 2: Lorenz Attractor
Domenic Murtari (domenic.murtari@gmail.com)

Default Parameters for the Lorenz Attractor:
s = 1
b = 2.66666
r = 28

CONTROLS:
* Esc to exit
* - to zoom out
* + to zoom in 
* Arrow Keys to change view
* s (lowercase s) to decrease loranz parameter s by 1
* S (capital s) to increase parameter s by 1
* b (lowercase b) to decrease loranz parameter b by .1
* B (capital b) to increase parameter b by .1
* r (lowercase r) to decrease loranz parameter r by 1
* R (capital r) to increase parameter r by 1
* 0 to reset view and parameters